parameters:
Complete the quest Help with Farming in the Nearby
Village by harvesting crops four times!!
Harvested the crops.

Quest [HelpingwithFarmWorkintheNearbyVillage]
Completed!!
Obtained a reward of 1000 EXP, 800G, and 2 fame.

\nw[Married man]Did you come to help again? Please stay overnight
this time too.
\nw[Kuno]Yes, I'll be in your care.
\nw[Married man]Thank you for helping me with various things.

\nw[Kuno]Various things? I thought it was just about the
harvest?

\nw[Married man]Did you come to help again? Was there anything
strange?

\nw[Kuno]What do you mean by strange? I don't mind the
smell of the countryside...
\nw[Married man]Hmmm, it doesn't seem like you're lying...

\nw[Married man]H-Hey, you came to help again. Was there anything
strange?

\nw[Kuno]I don't think there was anything strange... Did
something happen?
\nw[Married man]No, no, if there's nothing, then it's fine.

\nw[Married man]I'm grateful that you're helping me. Everywhere
needs extra hands during this time.

\nw[Married woman]I never expected to have a child. Other children
in the neighborhood are also pregnant, so it seems
like things will be tough from now on.

\nw[Married woman]Phew... Maybe I've been working too much. Lately,
my body feels heavy.
\nw[Married woman]That person could use a little more planning.
Harvested the crops.
Harvested the crops.
Harvested the crops.
Harvested the crops.
Harvested the crops.

\nw[Newlywed Woman]We have a child now. It's a busy time, but I have
to take a break... I'm sorry, but please
understand.

\nw[Newlywed Woman]Hmm, lately I've been feeling a little off
physically.

\nw[Newlywed Woman]Hehe, it looks like we'll have a good harvest this
year

\nw[Newlywed Man]Hey, you came again. It's good to stay over after
work today too.
\nw[Kuno]Yeah, I'll be in your care.

\nw[Newlywed Man]I'll be the one taking care of you down there...
hehehe

\nw[Newlywed Man]You came to work as a masseuse again this time,
didn't you?
\nw[Kuno]Yeah, leave it to me.
\nw[Newlywed Man]...Is she just slow?
\nw[Newlywed Man]Y-You...!

\nw[Kuno]Why are you making such a strange face? Don't
worry, I'm doing my job properly.
\nw[Newlywed Man]Ah, ah...

\nw[Newlywed Man]I just got married, you know. I have to show that
I can be reliable here!
\nw[Unmarried Man]Yo! You came back again, huh? I'll welcome you!

\nw[Kuno]Are you in that much trouble? Well, since it's
work, I'll help you out.

\nw[Unmarried Man]I'm looking forward to the night. It can't compare
to being with her... hehe
\nw[Unmarried Man]Oh, don't tell me you haven't noticed?
\nw[Kuno]What do you mean by 'haven't noticed'?

\nw[Unmarried Man]Oh, sorry, sorry. It was a case of mistaken
identity. I'm just busy with work, so I
misunderstood a bit!
\nw[Unmarried Man]Ah... um... O-Okay
\nw[Kuno]What's wrong? You're acting suspiciously.

\nw[Unmarried Man]No, uh, yeah. I'm in the middle of work, so don't
worry about it!

\nw[Unmarried Man]My girlfriend came to help with the family
business. This might be a step towards
marriage...!

\nw[Unmarried woman]No way... I can't believe I'm pregnant... Ugh,
does this mean I have to get married here...

\nw[Unmarried woman]Hmm, I wonder... It seems like my period is
late...

\nw[Unmarried woman]Hmm, there are so many bugs here. I'm a little
scared...

\nw[Villager]Oh my, the number of pregnant girls suddenly
increased. It's going to get lively around here.

\nw[Villager]Thank you, young ones, for helping us. We really
appreciate it.

\nw[Villager]Lately, the guys seem to be more motivated. It's a
good thing.
\nw[Villager]Can't beat the passage of time, huh?
There is no need for me here now.
There is no need for me to be here now.
There is no need for me to be here now.
There is no need for me to be here now.
There is no need to leave the village now.
\nw[Villager]Good work, good work! I'll do my best~
\nw[Villager]I won't lose, no matter what!
